gr-bladerf (1.0.0) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian packaging using dpkg-buildpackage and dh + cmake.
    Produces a single binary package gr-bladerf containing the
    gnuradio-bladeRF shared library, PyBind11 Python bindings,
    GRC YAML block descriptions, public headers and CMake config
    files.

